|               |                         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |                           DataSourceExec: file_groups={1 group: [[/data/nation/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex]]}, projection=[n_name, n_nationkey], file_type=vortex                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |                     CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |                       HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(o_orderkey@7, l_orderkey@2)], projection=[c_acctbal@0, c_address@1, c_comment@2, c_custkey@3, c_name@4, c_nationkey@5, c_phone@6, l_discount@8, l_extendedprice@9]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
