|               |                             ProjectionExec: expr=[c_acctbal@1 as c_acctbal, c_address@2 as c_address, c_comment@3 as c_comment, c_custkey@4 as c_custkey, c_name@5 as c_name, c_nationkey@6 as c_nationkey, c_phone@7 as c_phone, o_orderkey@0 as o_orderkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                               CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |                                 HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(o_custkey@0, c_custkey@3)], projection=[o_orderkey@1, c_acctbal@2, c_address@3, c_comment@4, c_custkey@5, c_name@6, c_nationkey@7, c_phone@8]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |                                   CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
